


cont_mat(1)                    Scilab Function                    cont_mat(1)






NAME
  cont_mat - controllability matrix

CALLING SEQUENCE
  [cc]=cont_mat(A,B)
  [cc]=cont_mat(sl)

PARAMETERS

  a,b       : two real matrices of appropriate dimensions

  sl        : linear system (syslin list)

DESCRIPTION
  cont_mat returns the controllability matrix of the pair A,B (resp. of the
  system sl=[A,B,C,D]).
  cc=[B, AB, A^2 B,..., A^(n-1) B]

SEE ALSO
  ctr_gram




































